# radroots-replica-sync-wasm

Wasm bindings for replica synchronization interfaces for Rad Roots data layers.

## Goals

- expose wasm-callable sync and ingest entry points for replica workflows
- keep request parsing and result marshaling deterministic in web runtimes
- integrate replica synchronization flows with wasm SQL executor surfaces
- provide stable bridge interfaces for higher-level Rad Roots web clients

